data.description: Stone home sitting atop 2.39 acres offers privacy without the drive to town. Natural light fills home through out the year. Entry level features plenty of space to entertain, and lighting updates in kitchen and den. Floorplan offer multiple options to make this home your own. Good size bedrooms upstairs. 2 tier of septic system pumped in January 2024. Recently installed Rhino Water Softener System and Leaf Guard Seamless Gutters. Detached, no door to home from garage, 2 car garage with loft that is used for storage. Lower Driveway is an easement and neighbor maintains, owner just responsible once you turn onto property at hair pin turn. DRIVEWAY IS STEEP but at house is level. There is parking at bottom for bad weather if needed
